@model ShareSpace.Models.Client.Client
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Index";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_ClientDashboardLayout.cshtml";
}

<div class="content__inner content__inner--sm">
	<header class="content__title">
		<h1>@Model.FirstName @Model.LastName</h1>
		<small>Web/UI Developer, Edinburgh, Scotland</small>
	</header>

	<div class="card profile">
		<div class="profile__img">
			<img src="/img/avatar/avatar1.jpg" alt="@Model.FirstName">
		</div>

		<div class="profile__info">
			<p>Cras mattis consectetur purus sit amet fermentum. Maecenas sed diam eget risus varius blandit sit amet non magnae tiam porta sem malesuada magna mollis euismod.</p>

			<ul class="icon-list">
				<li><i class="fa fa-phone"></i> @Model.MobileNo</li>
				<li><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i> @Model.Email</li>
				<li><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i> @Model.FirstName</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="toolbar">
		<nav class="toolbar__nav">
			<a class="active" href="../Dashboard/Index">About</a>
		</nav>

		<div class="actions">
			<i class="actions__item zmdi zmdi-search" data-sa-action="toolbar-search-open"></i>
		</div>

		<div class="toolbar__search">
			<input type="text" placeholder="Search...">

			<i class="toolbar__search__close zmdi zmdi-long-arrow-left" data-sa-action="toolbar-search-close"></i>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="card">
		<div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-body__title mb-4">About @Model.FirstName @Model.LastName</h4>

			<p>Pellentesque vitae quam quis tellus dignissim faucibus. Suspendisse mattis felis at faucibus lobortis. 
				Sed sit amet tellus dolor. Fusce quis sollicitudin velit. Praesent gravida ullamcorper lectus et tincidunt. 
				Phasellus lectus quam, porta pharetra feugiat in, auctor eget dolor.</p>


            <br>

			<h4 class="card-body__title mb-4">Contact Information</h4>

			<ul class="icon-list">
				<li><i class="fa fa-phone"></i>@Model.MobileNo</li>
				<li><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>@Model.Email</li>
				<li><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i>@Model.FirstName</li>
				<li><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i>@Model.FirstName</li>
				<li><i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i>5470 Madison Street Severna Park, MD 21146</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>